summary: Solving customer's problems creates value. Being an agile enthousiast I'm passionate about doing that by delivering relevant digital products to customers iteratively. As an analyst and product owner, I ensure short feedback loops with stakeholders to analyse, challenge and prioritize their requirements. That enables me to define minimum viable products which are aligned with business goals and technically feasable. Having a lean mindset, I'm constantly looking for ways to learn and improve. Additionally I'm designing and giving training courses on various product topics, e.g. Design Thinking.
